PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for the purposes of the Atlantic Canada Opportunities Agency Act of FRANK MacINNIS of Creignish, Nova Scotia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Enterprise Cape Breton Corporation to hold office for a term of three years, in the place of Robert McFadgen.
